attachments.title: Here's the full lineup of Nacho Week 2016 restaurants and dishes
attachments.text: Starting Sept. 18, The Oregonian/OregonLive will host its second annual Nacho Week, with a dozen Portland restaurants offering nacho specials for $10 or less. Readers who eat their way through a certain number of nachos and fill out their Nacho Passport (coming soon) will be eligible for prizes.
